text: The All-Ukrainian Union "Democrats" () is a political party in Ukraine registered in January 1996. Official databases of political parties in Ukraine of the Ukrainian Ministry of Justice Until 2013 it was named the Party of National Economic Development of Ukraine () Партія національно-економічного розвитку України (ПНЕРУ), Обрій During the 1998 elections the party won no seats, in the 2002 elections the party won 1 (single-mandate constituency) seat. In the 2006 elections and the 30 September 2007 elections, the party failed to win parliamentary representation. The party did not participate in the 2012 parliamentary elections.
